summary: So someone uploaded the valentine’s video to YouTube. Guys, this is not okay. They want to keep that part of their life in...
body: So someone uploaded the valentine’s video to YouTube. Guys, this is not okay. They want to keep that part of their life in PRIVATE. we DO NOT have the right to invade people’s privacy. I don’t know why that person thought it was alright to upload something they tried to get rid off so hard. They are human. They are not toys, cartoon, or made for people’s entertainment. I’m so angry. Dan didn’t post that video for people to be like PHAN PROOF PHAN PROOF. He was the most vulnerable he has ever been. And this is how people pay him back? This is horrible. Like guys, yes I ship them, yes they look cute together, but I prefer them to be comfortable and respect them over everything. They deserve it.
